data.description: Discover luxury living situated in the gated community of Broadmoor Estates in Waterview. The gated entrance ensures security & exclusivity, setting the tone for the exceptional lifestyle that awaits within. This wonderful home is nestled on a golf course lot, with a sparkling pool with water features, offering breathtaking views from the 3rd fairway. With 5 bedrooms, 4 full baths, an office with a closet - that can be used as a 6th bedroom, plus an oversized living area-game room & a media room this home embodies the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, & entertainment. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, outfitted with stainless steel appliances, white cabinetry, & a spacious island. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or prefer casual dining, this kitchen is designed to cater to your every need. Come & enjoy a lifestyle that includes access to the finest amenities, exclusive community events, & the prestige of residing in one of Rowlett's most sought-after neighborhoods.
